The problem is you are adding a semicolon to your style.

The semicolon is only used by the CSS parser to know the breaks between then css values. You do not need one after the last value and you can not use them when setting a value in an element&#39;s style attribute.

I simplified your code to demonstrate.

*With the semicolon*

